  "title": "Karaoke Service Crew | Islandwide | Up to $2,800 + Monthly Performance Bonus",
  "description": "<p>💰 <strong>Salary:</strong> Basic + fixed OT + Variable Bonus + Staff Benefits<br />🕒 <strong>Shift:</strong> </p><p>Day Shift 11am to 9pm/ 10am to 8pm/ 12pm to 10pm</p><p>Night Shift 6:30pm to 3:30am/ 4:30pm to 1:30am <br /></p><p>🛎️ <strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p><ul><li>Welcome guests warmly and guide them to their reserved tables</li><li>Take and serve food & drink orders accurately and efficiently</li><li>Handle POS systems and phone inquiries with professionalism</li><li>Keep the environment clean and ensure guests have a top-tier experience</li><li>Work closely with your teammates and support smooth daily operations</li><li>Be comfortable around alcoholic beverages and nightlife vibes</li></ul><p>✅ <strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></p><ul><li>Prior F&B experience is a big plus</li><li>Friendly, energetic, and team-oriented attitude</li><li>Able to handle fast-paced service and nightlife crowd</li><li>Willing to work shifts</li></ul><p>🎁 <strong>What You’ll Get:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Performance Bonuses</strong></li><li><strong>Staff Meals & Benefits</strong></li><li><strong>Fun & energetic work culture</strong></li><li></li></ul><p>EA Personnel Name: Nicholas Wong</p><p>EA Personnel No: R23113643</p><p>EA License No: 23C1703</p>",
